This is true on Test at the moment. Whether or not is will remain that way until we patch next is uncertain. Right now, the plan is to leave it this way, but that plan could change so don't get too excited. <br>
<br>
The main reason for this change is to fix an 'exploit'. We are fully aware of the beneficial side of this change, and as of our last meeting we are inclined to keep that beneficial side as it is. <br>
<br>
Alan </b><br>
